oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Original wills, Atchison, Mary E., 1912 February 22
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: An original will of Mary E. Atchison, of Nashville, Tennessee, dated July 5th, 1889. Illustrates the first page of the document. Includes a notarized document of Warren County, Kentucky, dated Feb. 12th, 1912 and a Davidson County, Tennessee document, dated February 22nd, 1912. Forms part of Record Group 16, Original Wills, 1780-1925.
